org.eclipse.january.metadata

Class DynamicConnectionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.january.metadata.DynamicConnectionInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, MetadataType

    public class DynamicConnectionInfo
extends Object
implements MetadataType
    This metadata is set by a remote dataset. It provides information about dropped data and received data while the dataset is connected. Not all remote datasets are forced to provide this information. This class is set in bundle org.eclipse.dawnsci.remotedataset.client as metadata on RemoteDatasets returned from the Data Server
